a-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 19, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rdv1665702921790.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rdv1665702921790.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rdv1665702921790.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rdv1665702921790\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Access Profiles and Statistics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__access_profiles_and_statistics_140321\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The access profile is the sequence of all access paths needed by a user view.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__p_d45752e1_d45753e1_d45754e1\">In the following figures, an access profile is graphically represented by annotations on the entity boxes:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__li_d22922e1_d22923e1_d22924e1\">Single arrow—Indicates the direction of access and that only one occurrence of the entity is expected in an access path\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__li_d22925e1_d22926e1_d22927e1\">Double arrow—Indicates the direction of access and that several entity occurrences are expected to be accessed\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__li_d22928e1_d22929e1_d22930e1\">Number in the right-hand corner of the entity box—Indicates the access sequence of the entities, or the depth\n </li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__topic_d29722e1_d29723e1_d29724e1_d29725e1_d29726e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d642237e68\">\n                       \n Examples\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__p_d45758e1_d45759e1_d45760e1\">The following figure shows a simple access profile diagram for the access profile of the retrieval 'Find order 0024 and then find the company it is for.'</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__fig_d45761e1_d45762e1_d45763e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Access Profile for Single Occurrence</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Access Profile for Single Occurrence\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/accessprofilesingleocc.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__p_d45767e1_d45768e1_d45769e1\">The following illustration shows the access profile for 'Find the country USA and then find all companies that reside there':</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__fig_d45770e1_d45771e1_d45772e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 2. </span>Access Profile with Multiple Occurrences Expected</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Access Profile with Multiple Occurrences Expected\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/accessprofilemultipleoccs.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__p_d45776e1_d45777e1_d45778e1\">The following illustration shows the access profile where several companies are retrieved and, for each company, the country where the company is located. All the orders for each company must be retrieved. Note that both COUNTRY and ORDER are at level two.</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__fig_d45779e1_d45780e1_d45781e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 3. </span>Simple Access Profile</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Simple access profile\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/accessprofileexample.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__p_d45785e1_d45786e1_d45787e1\">Consider a more complicated example. In this example, information for a complete configuration needs to be retrieved. The access profile has been marked on the subset of the modeled entities in the following illustration:</p>\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__fig_d45788e1_d45789e1_d45790e1\"><figcaption><span class=\"fig--title-label\">Figure 4. </span>Complex Access Profile</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Complex access profile\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/accessprofileexample2.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__topic_d29727e1_d29728e1_d29729e1_d29730e1_d29731e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d642237e129\">\n                       \n Access profile statistics\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__p_d45797e1_d45798e1_d45799e1\">Access profile statistics show how many occurrences are accessed and how often the relationships are used. For example, the following table shows the statistics for the access profile used for retrieving a complete configuration.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Access profile statistics table</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n Access Path <a href=\"#fntarg_1\" name=\"fnsrc_1\"><sup>1</sup></a>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n Via <a href=\"#fntarg_2\" name=\"fnsrc_2\"><sup>2</sup></a>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n No. of selected occ.'s <a href=\"#fntarg_3\" name=\"fnsrc_3\"><sup>3</sup></a>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n Access stress value <a href=\"#fntarg_4\" name=\"fnsrc_4\"><sup>4</sup></a>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n &gt; CONFIGURATION\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n ID_CONFIGURATION\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 1\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n CONFIGURATION &gt;&gt; PART\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n ID_CONFIGURATION\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n 20\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 20\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n PART &gt; DELIVERYLINE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n ID_DELIVERY, ID_DELIVERYLINE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 20\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n DELIVERYLINE &gt;&gt; COVERED_ITEM\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n ID_DELIVERY, ID_DELIVERYLINE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n 3\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 60\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n COVERED_ITEM &gt; ORDERLINE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n ORDER_NR, ID_ORDERLINE\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 60\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1\">\n ORDERLINE &gt; MATERIAL\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2\">\n ID_MATERIAL\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 60\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"3\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__1 rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__2 rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__3\">\n Total Access Stress Rating <a href=\"#fntarg_5\" name=\"fnsrc_5\"><sup>5</sup></a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdv1665702921790__table_d4385e1_d4386e1_d4387e1__entry__4\">\n 221\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fn\"><a href=\"#fnsrc_1\" name=\"fntarg_1\"><sup>1</sup></a>  Access Path shows the entities involved (including the direction of access).</div><div class=\"fn\"><a href=\"#fnsrc_2\" name=\"fntarg_2\"><sup>2</sup></a>  Via shows the selection criteria for the occurrence.</div><div class=\"fn\"><a href=\"#fnsrc_3\" name=\"fntarg_3\"><sup>3</sup></a>  No. of selected occurrences indicates the average rate of occurrences expected to be selected using the selection criteria for an individual entity.</div><div class=\"fn\"><a href=\"#fnsrc_4\" name=\"fntarg_4\"><sup>4</sup></a>  Access Stress Value indicates the average number of occurrences expected to be selected based on previously retrieved occurrences for an individual entity.</div><div class=\"fn\"><a href=\"#fnsrc_5\" name=\"fntarg_5\"><sup>5</sup></a>  Total Access Stress Rating indicates the average number of occurrences expected to be selected for all entities.</div></article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531548\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Access Profiles and Statistics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 19, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Access Profiles and Statistics The access profile is the sequence of all access paths needed by a user view. In the following figures, an access profile is graphically represented by annotations on the entity boxes: Single arrow—Indicates the direction of access and that only one occurrence of the entity is expected in an access path Double arrow—Indicates the direction of access and that several entity occurrences are expected to be accessed Number in the right-hand corner of the entity box—Indicates the access sequence of the entities, or the depth Examples The following figure shows a simple access profile diagram for the access profile of the retrieval 'Find order 0024 and then find the company it is for.' Figure 1. Access Profile for Single Occurrence The following illustration shows the access profile for 'Find the country USA and then find all companies that reside there': Figure 2. Access Profile with Multiple Occurrences Expected The following illustration shows the access profile where several companies are retrieved and, for each company, the country where the company is located. All the orders for each company must be retrieved. Note that both COUNTRY and ORDER are at level two. Figure 3. Simple Access Profile Consider a more complicated example. In this example, information for a complete configuration needs to be retrieved. The access profile has been marked on the subset of the modeled entities in the following illustration: Figure 4. Complex Access Profile Access profile statistics Access profile statistics show how many occurrences are accessed and how often the relationships are used. For example, the following table shows the statistics for the access profile used for retrieving a complete configuration. Table 1. Access profile statistics table Access Path 1 Via 2 No. of selected occ.'s 3 Access stress value 4 > CONFIGURATION ID_CONFIGURATION 1 1 CONFIGURATION >> PART ID_CONFIGURATION 20 20 PART > DELIVERYLINE ID_DELIVERY, ID_DELIVERYLINE 1 20 DELIVERYLINE >> COVERED_ITEM ID_DELIVERY, ID_DELIVERYLINE 3 60 COVERED_ITEM > ORDERLINE ORDER_NR, ID_ORDERLINE 1 60 ORDERLINE > MATERIAL ID_MATERIAL 1 60 Total Access Stress Rating 5 221 1 Access Path shows the entities involved (including the direction of access). 2 Via shows the selection criteria for the occurrence. 3 No. of selected occurrences indicates the average rate of occurrences expected to be selected using the selection criteria for an individual entity. 4 Access Stress Value indicates the average number of occurrences expected to be selected based on previously retrieved occurrences for an individual entity. 5 Total Access Stress Rating indicates the average number of occurrences expected to be selected for all entities. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}